---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Laser Hair Removal | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Long‑term hair reduction for smoother, lower‑maintenance skin.", "canonical": "/services/laser-hair-removal", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{
    --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8; --accent:#0F766E;
  }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .side-label{
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    letter-spacing:.08em;
    font-variant-caps: all-small-caps;
    color: var(--muted);
    opacity:.9;
  }
  .sticky-top{ position: sticky; top: 6rem; }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  @media (max-width: 1023px){
    .side-col{ display:none; }
  }
  a.section-anchor{ text-decoration:none; color:inherit; }
  a.section-anchor:hover{ color: var(--accent); }
</style>

  <!-- HERO v2: left-aligned, with overline -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <nav class="text-sm muted mb-3">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-black">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-1">/</span>
        <a href="/services" class="hover:text-black">Services</a>
        <span class="mx-1">/</span>
        <span>Laser Hair Removal</span>
      </nav>
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] font-semibold tracking-tight">Laser Hair Removal</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[1.125rem] md:text-xl muted measure">Long‑term hair reduction for smoother, lower‑maintenance skin.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 h-px w-full border-t rule"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY: same Style P layout below -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
    <aside class="side-col col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
      <div class="sticky-top flex flex-col items-center gap-10">
        <a href="#description" class="side-label a11y section-anchor">Description</a>
        <a href="#benefits" class="side-label section-anchor">Benefits</a>
        <a href="#how" class="side-label section-anchor">How&nbsp;It&nbsp;Works</a>
        <a href="#process" class="side-label section-anchor">The&nbsp;Process</a>
        <a href="#care" class="side-label section-anchor">Pre&nbsp;/&nbsp;Post</a>
        <a href="#faqs" class="side-label section-anchor">FAQs</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">
      <section id="description" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Description</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 muted dropcap">
          This service focuses on refined, natural‑looking improvement. We start with a concise consultation to understand your goals, map your features, and ensure safety and candidacy.
          The plan is measured and realistic—aiming for harmony, not excess.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 muted">
          Technique, dosing, or device parameters are selected for your indication and timeline. We explain what the service can (and cannot) accomplish and when an alternative may suit better.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 muted">
          Benefits vary by indication, but most guests appreciate subtle polish, clear guidance, and a plan that respects both anatomy and lifestyle.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 muted">
          <li>Personalized mapping and measured technique</li>
          <li>Comfort‑forward approach and simple aftercare</li>
          <li>Transparent expectations and maintenance planning</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="how" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 muted">
          We match the modality to your mapped indication. That may involve refined dosing, device parameters, or staged visits.
          The approach balances efficacy with restraint so results look like you on a good day.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="process" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2>
        <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal pl-5 muted space-y-2">
          <li><span class="font-medium text-black">Consultation.</span> Goals, medical history, candidacy, and planning.</li>
          <li><span class="font-medium text-black">Treatment.</span> Technique tailored to indication and area with comfort in mind.</li>
          <li><span class="font-medium text-black">Review & maintenance.</span> What to expect, and when follow‑ups may help.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="care" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 muted">
          You’ll receive concise pre‑ and post‑care notes tailored to your service.
          In general, arrive with clean skin, avoid irritants when advised, and follow the simple do’s and don’ts we provide after your visit.
        </p>
        <h3 class="mt-4 font-medium">Before your visit</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted">
          <li>Avoid new actives/irritants if directed</li>
          <li>Disclose medications, allergies, procedures</li>
          <li>Hydrate and arrive with clean skin</li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="mt-4 font-medium">After your visit</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted">
          <li>Follow your specific post‑care steps</li>
          <li>Protect from heat/sun and skip harsh actives</li>
          <li>Reach out with any unexpected reactions</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 muted"><span class="font-medium text-black">How many sessions will I need?</span> It depends on your goals and indication. We outline a plan during your consultation.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 muted"><span class="font-medium text-black">Will it look natural?</span> Our approach favors harmony and restraint so results feel like you.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 muted"><span class="font-medium text-black">Is there downtime?</span> Most services have minimal downtime. We review specifics and aftercare that’s simple to follow.</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm muted">*Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.</p>
      </section>
    </article>

    <aside class="side-col col-span-2 lg:col-span-3 xl:col-span-4">
      <div class="sticky-top measure">
        <p class="muted"><strong>Good to know:</strong> We tailor technique, cadence, and aftercare to your timeline.</p>
        <p class="muted mt-4"><strong>Quality:</strong> Trained providers, premium sourcing, evidence‑informed protocols.</p>
        <p class="muted mt-4"><strong>Expectations:</strong> We set realistic timelines and support you with clear check‑ins.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
